<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ PAGE 2 — MY STORY ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="p2">
  <div class="gold-bar-top"></div>
  <div class="gold-bar-bottom"></div>
  <div class="page-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="page-label anim-1">Our Story</div>
      <h2 class="section anim-1">From India to Ohio to Loomis —<br>A Journey I Know By Heart</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule anim-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col anim-3">
      <div>
        <h3 class="sub">I know exactly what it feels like to be you right now.</h3>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">My name is Sunit Brar. I'm a REALTOR® and Placer County specialist — and a physician's spouse who has lived this relocation journey in its most real, unfiltered form.</p>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">My husband is a pulmonary and critical care physician. We moved from India to Ohio, where he completed his residency and fellowship, built a thriving private practice, and we put down roots for over a decade. I ran his medical office alongside raising our family. Then in 2019, we made the leap — closing his practice and starting over in California.</p>
        <div class="story-quote">"The hardest part? He moved first. I stayed behind in Ohio with our children until the school year ended."</div>
        <p class="body-text">I know the loneliness of that in-between time — one foot in the old life, one reaching toward the new. I know what it's like to pack up a home alone, to say goodbye to the community you built, and to arrive somewhere not knowing a single soul.</p>
        <div class="giving-box">A portion of every transaction I close is donated to a Parkinson's nonprofit — because giving back is at the heart of everything I do.</div>
      </div>
      <div>
        <h3 class="sub">What surprised me most — Loomis felt like home immediately.</h3>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">We found our home in Loomis — and something clicked right away. Loomis has the same quiet, country-adjacent charm as the Copley area of Ohio where we'd lived. A little away from the main suburbs, a little more space to breathe, oak trees instead of maples. It felt right.</p>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">And then I discovered something I hadn't expected — how wonderfully diverse and welcoming this community is. Sacramento and Placer County have thriving South Asian communities, Sikh gurdwaras, Hindu temples, Indian grocery stores, cultural events, and warm neighborhoods where my family felt seen and at home almost immediately.</p>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">The weather alone was a revelation after Ohio winters.</p>
        <h3 class="sub" style="margin-top:12px">Why I became a REALTOR®</h3>
        <p class="body-text">I became a REALTOR® because of this experience — because I wished someone had walked alongside me the way I now walk alongside physician families every single day. I understand this journey not as a professional who serves your niche, but as someone who has lived inside it. This guide is my gift to you.</p>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-top:10px;font-family:'Cormorant Garamond',serif;font-style:italic;font-size:clamp(11px,1.4vw,15px);color:var(--navy)">— Sunit Brar</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ══════════════════════════════════════ PAGE 3 — WHY SACRAMENTO ══════════════════════════════════════ -->
<div class="page" id="p3">
  <div class="gold-bar-top"></div>
  <div class="gold-bar-bottom"></div>
  <div class="page-inner">
    <div>
      <div class="page-label anim-1">The Region</div>
      <h2 class="section anim-1">Why Sacramento &amp; Placer County?</h2>
      <div class="gold-rule anim-2"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="stat-grid anim-2">
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">2.6M</div><div class="stat-lbl">Metro Population</div><div class="stat-sub">4th largest in CA</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">$530K</div><div class="stat-lbl">Median Home Value</div><div class="stat-sub">2.2% annual growth</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">269</div><div class="stat-lbl">Sunny Days/Year</div><div class="stat-sub">vs US avg of 205</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">#1</div><div class="stat-lbl">Relocation Destination</div><div class="stat-sub">Redfin News ranking</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">60%</div><div class="stat-lbl">Homeownership Rate</div><div class="stat-sub">Strong investment market</div></div>
      <div class="stat-card"><div class="stat-num">$91K+</div><div class="stat-lbl">Median HH Income</div><div class="stat-sub">+6.69% growth</div></div>
    </div>
    <div class="two-col anim-3" style="height:auto;margin-top:4px">
      <div>
        <h3 class="sub">A city on the rise</h3>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">Sacramento is one of California's most affordable major metros — and rapidly becoming a destination for medical professionals and families seeking quality of life without Bay Area prices.</p>
        <h3 class="sub">Farm-to-Fork Capital of America</h3>
        <p class="body-text" style="margin-bottom:8px">Over 40 farmers markets, world-class restaurants, and produce grown right in the region. For families who love fresh food and vibrant culture, this is a dream.</p>
